cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB 

This paper deals with cross-lingual natural language processing tasks and knowledge graphs, which are typically studied in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves training embedding models, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and database systems (cs.DB).
